    void
    MedicationCardDocument.addHl7InformationRecipient(POCDMT000040InformationRecipient value)
    Adds a hl7InformationRecipient
    A recipient of this CDA document (corresponds to the addressee of a letter - person or organization).Recipient types: - The main recipient of the document is indicated by typeCode 'PRCP' (primary recipient).Note: Since it makes no sense to create a CDA document without doing it for someone, in Switzerland at least one recipient MUST be declared.
